</section><section data-mw-section-id="18" id="mwAVM" aria-labelledby="Kecamatan"><div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Kecamatan">Kecamatan</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="//id.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Kota_Bekasi&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=18" title="Sunting bagian: Kecamatan" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>sunting</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="//id.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Kota_Bekasi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Sunting kode sumber bagian: Kecamatan"><span>sunting sumber</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r18844875" about="#mwt118" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" id="mwAVQ" data-mw="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;templatestyles&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;Module:Hatnote/styles.css&quot;},&quot;body&quot;:{&quot;extsrc&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;utama&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Templat:Utama&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Daftar kecamatan dan kelurahan di Kota Bekasi&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt118" id="mwAVU">Artikel utama: <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daftar_kecamatan_dan_kelurahan_di_Kota_Bekasi" title="Daftar kecamatan dan kelurahan di Kota Bekasi">Daftar kecamatan dan kelurahan di Kota Bekasi</a></div>
<p about="#mwt120" typeof="mw:Transclusion" id="mwAVY" data-mw="{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;:Daftar kecamatan dan kelurahan di Kota Bekasi&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Daftar_kecamatan_dan_kelurahan_di_Kota_Bekasi&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}">Kota Bekasi memiliki 12 kecamatan dan 56 kelurahan. Pada tahun 2017, jumlah penduduknya mencapai 2.409.083 jiwa dengan luas wilayah 206,61 km² dan sebaran penduduk 4.035 jiwa/km².<sup about="#mwt123" class="mw-ref reference" id="cite_ref-Permendagri-137-2017_24-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;ref&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Permendagri-137-2017&quot;},&quot;body&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;mw-reference-text-cite_note-Permendagri-137-2017-24&quot;}}"><a href="#cite_note-Permendagri-137-2017-24" id="mwAVc"><span class="mw-reflink-text" id="mwAVg"><span class="cite-bracket" id="mwAVk">[</span>21<span class="cite-bracket" id="mwAVo">]</span></span></a></sup><sup about="#mwt126" class="mw-ref reference" id="cite_ref-Permendagri-72-2019_25-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;ref&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Permendagri-72-2019&quot;},&quot;body&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;mw-reference-text-cite_note-Permendagri-72-2019-25&quot;}}"><a href="#cite_note-Permendagri-72-2019-25" id="mwAVs"><span class="mw-reflink-text" id="mwAVw"><span class="cite-bracket" id="mwAV0">[</span>22<span class="cite-bracket" id="mwAV4">]</span></span></a></sup></p><span about="#mwt120">

